																		Author Post - Can you do the Chickenswim Dance?
															</div>
				<div class="info">
					<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/decibelles" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2005044); return false;"  ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2005044&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610204272" alt="Decibelles" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2005044)"/></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/decibelles" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2005044); return false;" >Decibelles</a></span> <span class="odate time_1497748394 format_%25e%20%25b%20%25Y%2C%20%25H%3A%25M%7Cagohover">18 Jun 2017 01:13</span>
														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-2866892">
									

<p>Wrote this for the Christmas Exchange for <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/wrongjohnsilver" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2000367); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2000367&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1497748486" alt="WrongJohnSilver" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2000367)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/wrongjohnsilver" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2000367); return false;">WrongJohnSilver</a></span> in 2016, figured I'd post it. I don't like the idea that D-7924 is painted in other OMG stuff as mentally ill; I just think he's evil and twisted, and I wanted to lay the base for that. He's just evil.</p>
<p>Thanks to the following:</p>
<ul>
<li><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/wrongjohnsilver" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2000367); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2000367&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1497748486" alt="WrongJohnSilver" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2000367)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/wrongjohnsilver" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2000367); return false;">WrongJohnSilver</a></span> for liking it and suggesting a couple of changes.</li>
<li><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/doctor-cimmerian" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1414765); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1414765&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1497748486" alt="Doctor Cimmerian" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1414765)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/doctor-cimmerian" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1414765); return false;">Doctor Cimmerian</a></span> for giving critique even though he hated the tale due to taste stuff.</li>
<li><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/gaffney" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1324229); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1324229&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1497748486" alt="Gaffney" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1324229)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/gaffney" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1324229); return false;">Gaffney</a></span> for critiquing even though I 100% forgot what he suggested. I'm sure I implemented them.</li>
<li><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/photosynthetic" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(361873); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=361873&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1497748486" alt="Photosynthetic" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=361873)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/photosynthetic" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(361873); return false;">Photosynthetic</a></span> for writing the news report for me &lt;3</li>
<li><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/silberescher" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(304355); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=304355&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1497748486" alt="Silberescher" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=304355)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/silberescher" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(304355); return false;">Silberescher</a></span> for critique.</li>
<li><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/aiden-eldritch" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2221240); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2221240&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1497748486" alt="Aiden Eldritch" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2221240)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/aiden-eldritch" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2221240); return false;">Aiden Eldritch</a></span> for formatting help.</li>
</ul>
<p>What I listened to while writing: Nothing, really, but <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2CTbycx2Pfo">Whitehouse's Wriggle Like a Fucking Eel</a> fits the mood. Warning for possible seizure-inducing and epilepsy-inducing visuals, as well as loud noises.</p>

